FreeCodeCamp Sacramento

A website built by the Sacramento FreeCodeCamp community.

Photo by Jenny Arnez

Who We Are

We are a bunch of aspiring developers who wants to learn how to code. Our goals are to acquire new skills, network with like-minded individuals, and have a great time.

What We Do

We often gather at coffee houses to work on freecodecamp's open-source material. Helping and learning from others is what drives this community to support itself.

Get Started

Join us now by heading over to our Facebook page. Once you've done that you can head on over to freecodecamp.com and sign up for a free account and start coding!

We are an independent entity and not affliated with FreeCodeCamp, Inc.
